{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"fd781d23f2","title":"关于西北军区二月份应深入三反着重打虎的电报","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f206da5857","index":0,"year":1952,"month":2,"day":1,"articleId":"fd781d23f2"}],"tags":[{"id":"d5cbd05390","name":"通讯","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji31","name":"毛泽东全集第31卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/31-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji31":{"comments":[{"id":"a1c90f607b","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"fd781d23f2","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"习仲勋，当时任中国人民解放军西北军区政治委员。"}],"contents":[{"id":"d68705ba64","type":"title","text":"关于西北军区二月份应深人三反着重打虎的电报","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"fd781d23f2"},{"id":"a1c90f607b","type":"paragraph","text":"张宗逊同志，并告习仲勋同志","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"fd781d23f2"},{"id":"6e577696d8","type":"paragraph","text":"西北军区所属各级军区和客军二月全月应深入进行三反，着重反贪污，尤其着重打老虎，老虎不提净不许收兵，不许整编。你们叫三军“准备推识二月六日转业集训的时间”，没有明确指令二月全月进行三反。你们全区各部清出的贪污分子均很少，一亿元以上天老虎还未发动去提，并且连计划都还没有。望速做出打虎预算电告，并下动员令打虎","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"fd781d23f2"},{"id":"b3597a9ffd","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"fd781d23f2"},{"id":"2f9f33bc05","type":"paragraph","text":"二月一日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"fd781d23f2"},{"id":"cba9e295e6","type":"paragraph","text":"张宗逊，当时任中国人民解放军西北军区第一副司令员。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"fd781d23f2"}],"page":{"id":"37e351f242","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"fd781d23f2","start":322,"end":322}}}},"__N_SSG":true}